info.name: QUERY
info.value: SELECT distinct asa_ous.asa_project_code AS "Project code", asa_science.source_name AS "Source name", asa_science.ra AS "RA", asa_science.dec AS "Dec", asa_science.gal_longitude AS "Galactic longitude", asa_science.gal_latitude AS "Galactic latitude", asa_science.band_list AS "Band", to_number(asa_science.spatial_resolution) AS "Spatial resolution", asa_science.frequency_resolution AS "Frequency resolution", concat(concat(case when asa_science.ant_main_num > 0 then '12m' else '' end, case when asa_science.ant_aca_num > 0 then '7m' else '' end), case when asa_science.ant_tp_num > 0 then 'TP' else '' end) as "Array", (case when asa_science.is_mosaic = 'Y' then 'mosaic' else '' end) as "Mosaic", asa_science.int_time AS "Integration", to_char(dp_delivery_status.release_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS "Release date", asa_science.frequency_support AS "Frequency support", asa_science.velocity_resolution AS "Velocity resolution", asa_science.pol_products AS "Pol products", to_char(asa_science.start_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS "Observation date", asa_project.pi_name AS "PI name", asa_science.schedblock_name as "SB name", asa_project.coi_name AS "Proposal authors", min(asa_energy.sensitivity_10kms) AS "Line sensitivity (10 km/s)", asa_science.cont_sensitivity_bandwidth AS "Continuum sensitivity", asa_science.pwv AS "PWV", asa_ous.group_ous_uid as "Group ous id", asa_ous.member_ous_uid as "Member ous id", asa_science.asdm_uid AS "Asdm uid", asa_project.title AS "Project title", asa_project.type AS "Project type", asa_science.scan_intent AS "Scan intent", asa_science.fov AS "Field of view", asa_science.spatial_scale_max AS "Largest angular scale", dp_delivery_status.qa2_passed AS "QA2 Status", (select count(distinct asab.bibcode) from asa_project_bibliography asab where project_code = asa_ous.asa_project_code) AS "Pub", asa_project.science_keyword AS "Science keyword", asa_project.scientific_category AS "Scientific category", asa_ous.asa_project_code FROM alma.asa_science inner join alma.aqua_execblock on asa_science.asdm_uid = aqua_execblock.execblockuid inner join alma.asa_ous on asa_science.asa_ous_id = asa_ous.asa_ous_id inner join alma.asa_project on asa_ous.asa_project_code = asa_project.code left outer join alma.asa_project_bibliography on asa_ous.asa_project_code = asa_project_bibliography.project_code left outer join alma.dp_delivery_asdm_ous on asa_science.asdm_uid = dp_delivery_asdm_ous.asdm_uid left outer join alma.dp_delivery_status on dp_delivery_asdm_ous.deliverable_name = dp_delivery_status.delivery_id inner join alma.asa_energy on asa_science.dataset_id = asa_energy.asa_dataset_id WHERE (1=1) AND asa_science.product_type = 'MOUS' AND REGEXP_COUNT(aqua_execblock.qa0status, '(Semi)?Pass', 1, 'i') > 0 AND (dp_delivery_status.qa2_passed is null or dp_delivery_status.qa2_passed = 'Y') AND lower(asa_ous.asa_project_code) not like '%.csv' AND ( DEC BETWEEN -17.820014111111114 AND -17.81201411111111 AND RA BETWEEN 300.23368142980127 AND 300.24208440353203 AND (asin(sqrt((0.479441 - cx) * (0.479441 - cx) + (-0.822511 - cy) * (-0.822511 - cy) + (-0.305961 - cz) * (-0.305961 - cz)) / 2.0) < 0.000035)) AND (dp_delivery_status.release_date < to_date('2017-03-29', 'YYYY-mm-dd')) GROUP BY asa_ous.asa_project_code, asa_science.source_name, asa_science.ra, asa_science.dec, asa_science.gal_longitude, asa_science.gal_latitude, asa_science.band_list, asa_science.spatial_resolution, asa_science.frequency_resolution, asa_science.ant_main_num, asa_science.ant_aca_num, asa_science.ant_tp_num, asa_science.is_mosaic, asa_science.int_time, dp_delivery_status.release_date, asa_science.frequency_support, asa_science.velocity_resolution, asa_science.pol_products, asa_science.start_date, asa_project.pi_name, asa_science.schedblock_name, asa_project.coi_name, asa_science.cont_sensitivity_bandwidth, asa_science.pwv, asa_ous.group_ous_uid, asa_ous.member_ous_uid, asa_science.asdm_uid, asa_project.title, asa_project.type, asa_science.scan_intent, asa_science.fov, asa_science.spatial_scale_max, dp_delivery_status.qa2_passed, asa_project.science_keyword, asa_project.scientific_category, asa_science.footprint ORDER BY "Release date" asc

field.name: Project code
field.description: OUS Project Code

field.name: Source name
field.description: Name of the source as registered in the ASDM. Partial matches through wildcards (?, *), and boolean OR expressions ("|"), can be used.

field.name: RA
field.description: Right Ascension of the field pointing.

field.name: Dec
field.description: Declination of the field pointing.

field.name: Galactic longitude
field.description: Galactic longitude of the observation for RA/Dec. Estimated using PyEphem and RA/Dec.

field.name: Galactic latitude
field.description: Galactic latitude of the observation for RA/Dec. Estimated using PyEphem and RA/Dec.

field.name: Band
field.description: Space delimited list of bands

field.name: Frequency resolution
field.description: Estimated frequency resolution from all the spectral windows, using median values of channel widths.

field.name: Integration
field.description: Aggregated integration time for the field in the ASDM.

field.name: Frequency support
field.description: All frequency ranges used by the field

field.name: Velocity resolution
field.description: Estimated velocity resolution from all the spectral windows, from frequency resolution.

field.name: Pol products
field.description: Polarisation products provided.

field.name: PI name
field.description: case-insensitive partial match over the full PI name. Wildcards can be used

field.name: SB name
field.description: Name of the Scheduling Block used as a template for executing the ASDM containing this Field.

field.name: Proposal authors
field.description: Full name of CoIs .

field.name: Continuum sensitivity
field.description: Estimated noise in the aggregated continuum bandwidth. Note this is an indication only, it does not include the effects of flagging or dynamic range limitations.

field.name: PWV
field.description: Estimated precipitable water vapour from the XML_CALWVR_ENTITIES table.

field.name: Group ous id
field.description: Group OUS ID

field.name: Member ous id
field.description: Member OUS ID

field.name: Asdm uid
field.description: UID of the ASDM containing this Field.

field.name: Project title
field.description: Case-insensitive search over the project title

field.name: Project type
field.description: Project type.

field.name: Scan intent
field.description: Scan intent list for the observed field.

field.name: Field of view
field.description: Field of view (arcsec). Estimated from the frequency and antennas

field.name: Largest angular scale
field.description: Due to the fact that radio antennas can not be placed infinitely close, measurements do have a smallest separation which translates into a maximal angular distance beyond which features can not be resolved reliably any more. Adding observations with the ALMA Total Power array can add those missing largest scales.

field.name: QA2 Status
field.description: Quality Assessment 2 status: does the Member / Group OUS fulfil the PI's requirements?

field.name: ASA_PROJECT_CODE
field.description: OUS Project Code
